Great Portland to develop new Virgin store . British property development firm Great Portland Estates said on Monday that it would develop a new four level Virgin Megastore at King ' s Road , Chelsea . The 18 , 000 square feet store would be one of the largest in the UK . Virgin has agreed to take a new 25 - year lease at a starting rent of 310 , 000 stg per annum . Trading is expected to start in this autumn . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4366 
